# gen125 — bilingual ratchet for the affective register. Italian affective cues
# (tranquillo/imparerai for encouragement, parliamo in for a language offer) reach
# the same mod_chitchat branches as their English counterparts: the register
# competence lives in the cue set, not an English-only phrasebook.

# Italian encouragement.
> tranquillo, imparerai!
< Thanks — I'm learning as we go.

# Italian offer to switch language.
> ok parliamo in inglese
< We can chat in either language — I'll do my best.
